author: nokow
title: a nice object for collector
review:
Box/Instructions

Very nice numbered box, no instruction.

Parts

The minifig of each pack are different, so you can collect several pack.

Minifigures

The minifig are created with the parts from the minifig wall by the store employees

The build

No build, open the box and admire the figs

Overall opinion

I really love this little present from Lego, nice figs in a nice box.
